  "raw_html": "<main class=\"bd-main\" id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\">\n<div class=\"bd-content\">\n<div class=\"bd-article-container\">\n<div class=\"bd-header-article d-print-none\">\n<div class=\"header-article-items header-article__inner\">\n<div class=\"header-article-items__start\">\n<div class=\"header-article-item\">\n<nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"d-print-none\">\n<ul class=\"bd-breadcrumbs\">\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item breadcrumb-home\">\n<a aria-label=\"Home\" class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../index.html\">\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-home\"></i>\n</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../pytorch-api.html\">Reference API</a></li>\n<li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"../torch.html\">torch</a></li>\n<li aria-current=\"page\" class=\"breadcrumb-item active\">torch.hypot</li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"header-article-items__end\">\n<div class=\"header-article-item\">\n<div class=\"rating\">\n    Rate this Page\n    <div class=\"stars\">\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"1\" data-value=\"1\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"2\" data-value=\"2\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"3\" data-value=\"3\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"4\" data-value=\"4\">★</span>\n<span class=\"star\" data-behavior=\"tutorial-rating\" data-count=\"5\" data-value=\"5\">★</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"searchbox\"></div>\n<article class=\"bd-article\" id=\"pytorch-article\">\n<!-- Hidden breadcrumb schema for SEO only -->\n<div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<link href=\"../pytorch-api.html\" itemprop=\"item\"/>\n<meta content=\"Reference API\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"1\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<link href=\"../torch.html\" itemprop=\"item\"/>\n<meta content=\"torch\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"2\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n<div itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\n<meta content=\"torch.hypot\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"3\" itemprop=\"position\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"searchbox\"></div>\n<article class=\"bd-article\">\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"torch-hypot\">\n<h1>torch.hypot<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#torch-hypot\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">#</a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"torch.hypot\">\n<span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">torch.</span></span><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">hypot</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">input</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">other</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">*</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">out</span></span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span> <span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">→</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../tensors.html#torch.Tensor\" title=\"torch.Tensor\"><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span></a></span></span><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#torch.hypot\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">#</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Given the legs of a right triangle, return its hypotenuse.</p>\n<div class=\"math\">\n<span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math display=\"block\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mtext>out</mtext><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><msubsup><mtext>input</mtext><mi>i</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mo>+</mo><msubsup><mtext>other</mtext><mi>i</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup></mrow></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{out}_{i} = \\sqrt{\\text{input}_{i}^{2} + \\text{other}_{i}^{2}}\n\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"katex-html\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7651em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">out</span></span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3117em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">i</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.84em;vertical-align:-0.4804em;\"></span><span class=\"mord sqrt\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3596em;\"><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-3.8em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3.8em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\" style=\"padding-left:1em;\"><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">input</span></span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8719em;\